Gravity - tendency of an unstable note to descend
Magnetism - tendency of unstable note to more to the nearest stable pitch, a tendency that grows stronger the closer we get to a goal
Inertia - tendency of a pattern of musical motion to continue in the same fashion, where what is meant by "same" depends upon what that musical pattern is

